'''史提芬·占士·艾利蘭'''（{{lang-en|'''Stephen James Ireland'''}}，{{bd|1986年|8月22日|catidx=Ireland, Stephen}}）出生於-{[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]}-[[科克郡|科克郡]]的[[科布|科布]]，是一名職業足球員，擔任[[中場|中場]]。曾效力[[史篤城足球會|史篤城]]。

== 生平 ==
=== 曼城 ===
艾利蘭在出生及成長的[[科布|科布]]開展其球員事業，首先在其父米高（Michael Ireland）曾效力的{{tsl|en|Cobh Ramblers||科布漫步者}}（Cobh Ramblers）的少年隊參賽。而在學時期的史提芬·艾利蘭曾參加多隊[[英國|英國]]球隊的試訓，但由於他患有[[奧斯戈德氏病|奧斯戈德氏病]]（Osgood-Schlatter disease）而多不願冒險羅致。終於在15歲時加入[[曼城|曼城]]的青訓系統。

艾利蘭在2005年曾參與曼城一隊數場的季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]。於9月18日主場對[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]首次為一隊在正式比賽上陣，於完場前後補入替[[乔伊·巴顿|祖爾·巴頓]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4232408.stm |title=Man City 0-1 Bolton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-09-18 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2020-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228085529/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4232408.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。三日後在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]作客對[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡士打]]首次正選登場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/4258570.stm |title=Doncaster 1-1 Man City (aet) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-09-21 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2020-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226014839/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/4258570.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月2日主場2-0擊敗[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4277860.stm |title=Man City 2-0 Everton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-10-02 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2017-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130172940/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4277860.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是他首場正選在[[英超|英超]]上陣，其出色的表現使他獲選為最佳球員（Man of the Match），賽後更被領隊[[斯图尔特·皮尔斯|皮雅斯]]點名稱讚<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.unison.ie/irish_independent/stories.php3?ca=94&si=1480827&issue_id=13086 |title=Ireland impresses as City add to Everton woes |publisher=''Irish Independent'' |date=2005-10-03 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035412/http://www.unison.ie/irish_independent/stories.php3?ca=94&si=1480827&issue_id=13086 |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。其後6場比賽史提芬·艾利蘭繼續擔當正選，更為他贏得一紙直到2009年才屆滿的合約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Ireland signs new contract with City |url=http://www.rte.ie/sport/2005/1026/irelands.html |publisher=[[RTÉ|RTÉ]] |date=2005-10-26 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2007-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071021162324/http://www.rte.ie/sport/2005/1026/irelands.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。餘下的球季艾利蘭參與大約半數曼城的比賽，於4月在操練時觸傷小腿而提早「收咧」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2373913,00.html |title=Ireland blow for City |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-04-18 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308042034/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2373913,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[2005年至2006年英格蘭超級聯賽|2005/06年球季]]合共16次正選及12次後補上陣，未有取得入球。由於在上季有突破的表現，在休季期間包括[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]、[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]及[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]等球會均對這名小將表示有興趣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2386483,00.html |title=Ireland attracting interest |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-08-09 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924144040/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2386483,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]史提芬·艾利蘭季初只能在後備席等待機會，皮雅斯認為年青球員需要用實際表現爭取領隊的信任，才可以獲得正選的席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2397703,00.html |title=No man is an Ireland |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-12-11 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309130343/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2397703,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年拆禮物日作客[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，下半場78分鐘史提芬·艾利蘭離門20碼左腳「窩利」射入，一箭定江山兼在[[英超|英超]]「開齋」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6200147.stm |title=Sheff Utd 0-1 Man City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-27 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2019-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730194007/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6200147.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。史提芬·艾利蘭的第二個入球在另一支[[设菲尔德|设菲尔德]]球隊身上取得，2007年1月16日在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]第三圈主場對[[谢周三足球俱乐部|錫周三]]，完半場前接應[[乔伊·巴顿|祖爾·巴頓]]的傳球近門射入先拔頭籌，最終以2-1淘汰對手晉級<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2402659,00.html |title=City see off brave Owls |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-01-16 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309135038/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2402659,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。史提芬·艾利蘭開始鞏固其在中場的正選席位，雖然合約尚有18個月才屆滿，曼城已準備提高薪金續約留人<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2404955,00.html |title=Ireland earns fresh City terms |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-02-08 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084732/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2404955,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月18日足總盃第五圈作客3-1淘汰[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]，史提芬·艾利蘭於完場前射入決勝球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6349643.stm |title=Preston 1-3 Man City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-18 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2007-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070829112857/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/6349643.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]領隊[[罗伊·基恩|堅尼]]十分欣賞這位同是來自[[科克|科克]]的小師弟，但史提芬·艾利蘭於2007年4月12日與曼城簽訂四年新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2410856,00.html |title=Ireland commits to City |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-04-12 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084742/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_2410856,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭超級聯賽|2007/08年球季]][[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|艾歷臣]]取代[[斯图尔特·皮尔斯|皮雅斯]]執掌曼城<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/6241052.stm |title=Eriksson named Man City manager |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-07-06 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2014-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418185210/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/6241052.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，史提芬·艾利蘭認為其新收購的球員將大大增強球隊的攻力<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_2662104,00.html |title=Ireland: We'll play flair |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-08-15 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010630/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_2662104,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這本來是史提芬·艾利蘭振翅高飛的一年，但他卻在[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|國家隊]]及球會惹來不斷的爭議。季初一切發展順利，2007年11月5日主場對[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]，下半場67分鐘史提芬·艾利蘭射穿[[奇治·哥頓|哥頓]]的「大小龍門」，曼城憑這入球小勝1-0，保持開季主場全勝及在聯賽榜上升到第3位；但史提芬·艾利蘭在入球後隨即退下短褲，露出印有[[超人|超人]]（Superman）[[商標|標誌]]的內褲<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7065173.stm |title=Man City 1-0 Sunderland |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-05 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017011712/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7065173.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他這個慶祝的舉動引起非議，由於這場比賽透過[[電視|電視]]現場直播，賽後艾歷臣擔心史提芬·艾利蘭會因此被罰<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2863729,00.html |title=Sven fears for Ireland |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-11-05 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924140037/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2863729,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終[[英格蘭足球總會|足總]]以其沒有露出[[臀|臀]]部，決定只作警告了事<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2864894,00.html |title=Ireland escapes punishment |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-11-06 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308021713/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2864894,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月24日主場對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]，史提芬·艾利蘭在完場前受傷補時射入致勝球，2-1獲勝兼延續主場全勝氣勢<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7099692.stm |title=Man City 2-1 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-24 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026223952/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7099692.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩星期後作客對[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]，離完場尚餘8分鐘，雙方仍然1-1平手，史提芬·艾利蘭向[[李榮杓|李榮杓]]作出雙腳飛剷攔截，被球證直接出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場，熱刺的[[杰梅恩·迪福|-{zh-hans:杰梅恩·迪福; zh-hk:迪科爾;}-]]隨即射入奠定勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7122809.stm |title=Tottenham 2-1 Man City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-12-09 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2019-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802215951/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7122809.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後艾歷臣承認判決合理<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2957606,00.html |title=Sven accepts Ireland red |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-12-09 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310080131/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2957606,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，史提芬·艾利蘭亦迅速向領隊對因此導致球隊落敗而道歉<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/article562870.ece |title=Villain says sorry to boss |publisher=《[[太陽報|''The Sun'']]》 |date=2007-12-10 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2015-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529073139/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/article562870.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>。下半季曼城成績急速下滑，雖然在「[[曼徹斯特打吡|曼徹斯特打吡]]」主客兩勝[[曼聯|曼聯]]，排名由有力爭標跌至聯賽榜中游。2008年3月16日史提芬·艾利蘭在次循環主場對[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]以入球洗擦被逐的不快記憶，下半場60分鐘近門射入披平1-1，最終2-1獲勝報卻一敗之辱，取得自去年12月中以來在主場聯賽的首場勝仗<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7284987.stm |title=Man City 2-1 Tottenham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-16 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814192634/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7284987.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月26日主場對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]史提芬·艾利蘭再下一城，開賽後10分鐘在禁區外左路「灣」入球門右上角先開紀錄，但曼城在領先2-0後最終反輸2-3<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7356044.stm |title=Man City 2-3 Fulham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-26 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2009-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028062917/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7356044.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。無心戀戰的曼城在煞科日作客1-8慘敗於[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]腳下<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7381794.stm |title=Middlesbrough 8-1 Man City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-11 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2018-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180520193229/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7381794.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。史提芬·艾利蘭以4個入球及1面[[紅牌|紅牌]]結束這個充滿爭議的球季。季後艾歷臣被炒而由[[馬克·曉士|馬克·曉士]]接掌帥印<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7431155.stm |title=Hughes becomes Man City manager |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-05 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129021248/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7431155.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然再有傳言史提芬·艾利蘭將會轉投[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]，但曉士澄清沒有其事<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3960806,00.html |title=Hughes not selling Ireland |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-08-10 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010543/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3960806,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2008年至2009年英格蘭超級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]展開，2008年8月24日史提芬·艾利蘭在主場3-0擊敗[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]貢獻兩次助攻<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7570609.stm |title=Man City 3-0 West Ham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-24 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116094243/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7570609.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後他重申留隊的意願<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4051915,00.html |title=Ireland - I want to stay at City |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-08-26 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010728/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4051915,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月30日作客[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]取得本季首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7578481.stm |title=Sunderland 0-3 Man City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-30 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103175108/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7578481.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後曼城以天價羅致[[羅賓奴|羅賓奴]]後令人期待會有好成績出現<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7593026.stm |title=Man City beat Chelsea to Robinho |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-01 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702234242/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7593026.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在6-1大炒[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]及升上聯賽榜第5位後，隊中各人士氣大增<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4180333,00.html |title=Ireland - We feel invincible |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-09-22 |accessdate=2009-05-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010940/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4180333,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 He scored again the in 2–2 draw at [[Newcastle_United_F.C.|Newcastle United]] on [[20_October|20 October]]. He scored both goals in the 2–2 draw at [[Hull_City_F.C.|Hull City]] on [[16_November|16 November]],<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1086394/Hull-City-2-Manchester-City-2-Hart-break-England-good-break-Ireland.html?ITO=1490 Hart break England good break Ireland] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1086394/Hull-City-2-Manchester-City-2-Hart-break-England-good-break-Ireland.html?ITO=1490 |date=20161002123731 }}. ''Daily Mail''</ref>and opened the score in the successive league match against [[Arsenal_F.C.|Arsenal]]. After netting in a 2-1 win over Everton, Ireland took his seasons tally to 13 in a memorable season for the Irishman.

=== 维拉 ===
2010年8月18日曼城俱乐部宣布爱尔兰作为[[詹姆斯·米尔纳|米尔纳]]转会的一部分加盟[[阿斯顿维拉|阿斯顿维拉]]，这也是其职业生涯效力的第二家球会。但他一直未能融入球隊，在傷兵滿營的維拉中場線，上半季僅獲派上陣10場。2011年1月31日終獲外借到[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]直到球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/9381428.stm |title=Newcastle sign Stephen Ireland on loan from Aston Villa |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-31 |accessdate=2011-02-02 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66YJpW57q?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/9381428.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

